OL,6,FA man who claimed he was groomed and
OL,7,Fabused by a paedophile priest at a Co
OL,8,FDown school is to receive #170,000 in
OL,9,Fdamages.
OL,11,FThe payout forms part of a settlement
OL,12,Freached today in his High Court action
OL,13,Fover historic physical and sexual
OL,14,Fassaults inflicted by the late Father
OL,15,FMalachy Finegan.
OL,17,FHe will also be given a written
OL,18,Fapology from the head of the Catholic
OL,19,FChurch in Ireland, his lawyer
