OL,6,FThe 57-year-old man, who cannot be
OL,7,Fidentified, sued the Diocese of
OL,8,FDromore and the Board of Governors at
OL,9,FSt Colman's College in Newry over
OL,10,Ffailures to protect him from the
OL,11,Fpriest.
OL,13,F"Malachy Finegan took a vulnerable boy
OL,14,Fand a vulnerable time in my life,
OL,15,Fgroomed me and then abused me for his
OL,16,Fown pleasure," he said after the case
OL,17,Fsettled.
OL,19,FReferred to as CA, he was a pupil at
OL,20,FSt Colman's between 1979 and 1985.
