OL,6,FDuring that period Finegan, who taught
OL,7,Fand worked at the college, molested
OL,8,Fhim under the guise of providing
OL,9,Fpastoral care, it was claimed.
OL,11,FThe priest was accused of a long
OL,12,Fcampaign of child sexual abuse but
OL,13,Fnever prosecuted or questioned by
OL,14,Fpolice about claims made against him.
OL,16,FFinegan died in 2002, but in 2018 it
OL,17,Femerged that the Diocese of Dromore
OL,18,Fhad settled a previous claim made by
OL,19,Fone of his alleged victims.
